</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install reverse gear (1) to countershaft (2) using bearing puller (3) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520066.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "37.952mm" ver = "01" gw = "115" gh = "91"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install 1st gear spacer (1) using special tool and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B033">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09940-54910">
09940–54910
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520067.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.479mm" ver = "01" gw = "103" gh = "129"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install 1st gear needle bearing and apply transaxle oil to it, and then install 1st gear synchronizer inner ring (2), 1st gear synchronizer center cone (3), 1st gear synchronizer outer ring (4) and 1st gear (1) to countershaft.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Make sure claws on 1st gear synchronizer center cone fit into the holes on 1st gear.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW101520027.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "58.219mm" ver = "01" gw = "146" gh = "149"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install low speed sleeve &#38; hub assembly (1) using special tool and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Support lower speed synchronizer hub using special tool as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Make sure that synchronizer ring key protrusion (5) are aligned with keys while press-fitting sleeve &#38; hub assembly.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check free rotation of 1st gear (3) after press-fitting sleeve &#38; hub assembly.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B034">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09944-77030">
09944–77030
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
